<h2>decktech.net</h2><b>location of article:</b> <hr>SWCCGPC.com News - spoiler alert posted by scott on Sun Jul 1 2007 <br>The Star Wars CCG Players Committee is geared up for some big summer news. In the next week or so we will release a new Advanced Rulebook for the game! Gone will be the days of having to look through multiple rules supplements! <br />
<br />
A new virtual set releases on July 22!  For updated news related to this announcement, please visit www.swccgpc.com.<br />
<br />
Here is a pre-release spoiler from the upcoming virtual set 13.<br />
<br />
Through The Force Things You Will See (V) 3<br />
[Virtual Set 13 - Dagobah - R] <br />
<br />
OUT OF PLAY INTERRUPT <br />
Text: If you are about to recirculate during your turn, and you have fewer cards in Used Pile than Force Pile, place your Used Pile under your Force Pile instead. OR Place the top card of your Used Pile on top of your Force Pile. <br />
Set Icon 13•X<br />
